title: RWBY Official Singles
description:
These are all the songs from the recent series by rooster teeth called RWBY or Red White Black Yellow. This is an awesome anime, and the composer/artist for the music in this anime is just as awesome. Jeff Williams is an awesome guy making sweet tunes for this anime and for rooster teeth in general. His Daughter Casey Lee Williams is featured in all of these songs, and she has an angelic, beautiful voice, being the final touch all of these songs need. These songs include:

Red Like Roses - Red Trailer

Mirror Mirror -  White Trailer

From Shadows  -  Black Trailer

I Burn     -     Yellow Trailer

If You need any kind of music that is hard to find on the internet, shout it out in the comments and I will find what you're looking for. I have been doing this for a couple of years unfortunately. I need to get paid more *sigh*.

-TalkingMuff1n
